```javascript
function convertCurrency(amount, from_currency, to_currency) {
    return (amount * 1000) / 1609;
}
```
In this conversion function, the variable "(amount * 1000) / 1609" represents the amount in cents, which then gets multiplied by . 5, and divided by 6, since there are 6 euros per pound.

